long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Omnea extension enables you to view desired content in 3D environment in omnea.xyz

This extension adds "View in 3d" button to supported websites for easier reach to dedicated content.

Omnea Extension doesn't show ads and send users' data anywhere.
